NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Judy made a very nice 3NT bid which Stan should be very happy about. Now his @sQ is worth something, since Judy is showing spade points. He has a nice heart suit which could easily generate 3 or 4 tricks. And he has clubs making it likely their side has lots of club tricks. So pass is very clear. |
